reviewText: This DVD's production is so low budget that on all of the wide angle shots the peoples faces are super fuzzy. Or how about the players in the DVD missing all kinds of easy shots. Not to mention, the coach likes to say "umm" like 10,000 times during the video. I wouldn't want this trash if it were free, so since I paid $32 I quickly returned it for a refund....it's that bad!!!
